will hold President Slobodan Milosevic responsible if the three
Americans are harmed or mistreated.
</P>
<P>
-- Ten days into the allied bombing campaign over Yugoslavia,
stakes are growing for Clinton. The resolute president, who has
few options and many risks, is up late and up early on the line
