before China resumes sovereignty over Macao on December 20.
</P>
<P>
The countdown clock at the Tianjin Railway, the brainchild of
the Tianjin Municipal Information Office, shows the number of days
remaining before the turnover.
</P>
<P>
Tianjin, one of four municipalities directly under the central
government, will be a key city hosting grand celebrations for the
event.
</P>
<P>
Another countdown clock is prominently displayed in Beijing's
Tiananmen Square.  
