around Beijing area to protect the Chinese capital from shifting
sand blown from the northwestern deserts.
</P>
<P>
Over the next ten years the province is expected to plant 337,
500 hectares of trees and transform about 6,700 hectares of low-
quality forest to the north and west of Beijing.
