Meanwhile, he said Albania would develop its relations with
France which used to have closer ties with Serbia.
</P>
<P>
Josselin promised that France would provide humanitarian aid
for the Kosovo refugees flooding into Albania and his government
was examining a request for global assistance in the Albanian
economy.
