<HEADLINE> World Cup Champion Wang Nan Tops Chinese Best Ten Athletes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 2 (Xinhua) -- World Cup table-tennis women's
champion Wang Nan topped the Chinese Best Ten Athletes of the Year
at a poll voted by 20 media press here on Thursday.
</P>
<P>
Wang, who captured four gold medals at the Bangkok Asian Games,
accumulated most votes from 10 million sports fans and
sportswriters across the nation.
</P>
<P>
Out of the top ten, nine were women athletes, including Wang
Nan (table-tennis), Li Xuemei (track and field), Sun Tianni (
weightlifting), Liu Xuan (gymnastics), Lee Lai Shan (windsurfing),
Chen Hua (swimming), Ye Zhaoying (badminton), Yang Yang (short-
track speed skating) and Ge Fei (badminton).
</P>
